## Known bugs
- (compose bug) keyboard does not show up when clicked on a already focused text field (change screens, switch between text inputs or close and reopen bottom sheet to workaround)

## Features
- viewmodels and API configuration improvements [#10](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/10) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/1fc2b52ab3dd346304b8507b43a626ee24a64e73))
- consistent components [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/ddc9d7fcf8b763916ca683c9b0e0fde281f4acbb))
- use material3 segmented buttons [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/27c2310b82e777309a794508cb20df78ea848518))
- use material3 bottom sheet [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/f35e151e46b617f8aab284b08f500fe1d0abe17a))
- **add-word-sheet**: open keyboard when shown & improve design [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/eca5553aeefd2dcc8f1760a78bdb3f41be63e0ef))
- make toasts not dismissable by default [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/56437aacb65f2696180813029821a5b92118e297))
- **dashboard**: improve design [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/b66b62fcea95ebf655b575d90db8b6199d6d124e))
- use material 3 pull to refresh [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/44d3049edc768d12743b65ac4d838aad8ae60a22))
- navigation rail for wide screens & display cutout padding [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/33c6267a483442f9212b9668f810c1d73a603f79))
- improve splash screen & wait for initial api connection [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/9edf824c4ea7bf6e0565fc16b6587c8c9f3be0d6))
- add user agent header [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/22086caaeb2efb4b169ad6e52a0afe76edbd0a10))
- logs [#12](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/12) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/97a64a0cd44e28292ebe0931ba8ab904dd896b5c))
- **api**: ability to migrate [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/fefa918bd2d57f0882d6e6a6fd38545b903c0840))

## Bug Fixes
- **chat-screen**: remove word item animations [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/9c2610c2646f044d3c7777ef697ee87289ba9c7b))
- RTL layout fixes [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/de079ac279d27a4b2fc772a7b2fe92772a0d0b0e))

## Chores
- update dependencies [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/c9bb9e4803995a6ed5e8fccc485989f09cabeae0))
- update dependencies [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/4f57d03214a51c9b4e23d3bc3d5a27f03ba02825))
- update version to v1.9.0 [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/14b0b6dd7ae8dc59f4710690db0488dd4680d27d))
- merge `dev` branch into `main` [#11](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/pull/11) ([aliernfrog](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/3d4edfa29ab170d4bef0bb01d557d0cbb4cbeeb5))

View this release on [GitHub](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/releases/tag/v1.9.0)
